Without doubt Chris Rea is one the most important and most high-powered blues and rock musician of the last 30 years. In his unprecedented career he looks back meanwhile at 19 albums and more than 22 millions sold sound carriers. Reason enough to unite his biggest hits on "Fool If You Think It's Over - The Definitive Greatest Hits", a collection of songs recorded between 2001 and 2008, including re-recordings of 6 of his best-known hits, with a new brilliant sound.
